('015ddd00-e94b-461f-b4da-e19c44c325a7', '92276b73-dca7-4e8f-958c-999ca8ced377', 'adfb2457-819c-4574-ace1-56f5b38d8f96', NULL, '2017-05-15', '', '18:30', '', 'dresden', 'Eritrea – das kleine Land am Roten Meer', 'Eritrea hat nach offiziellen Angaben 5 Millionen Einwohner. Mindestens die Hälfte der jungen Generation ist jedoch schon aus dem Land geflohen. Was sind die Gründe dafür? Im Vortrag wird die aktuelle Situation Eritreas beleuchtet, die Geschichte, Kultur(en) und Religionen des Landes benannt und die Zukunftsaussichten erörtert.\r\n\r\n1 x | 2 UE | gebührenfrei\r\n17F 1305\r\nMo, 15.05., 18.30 – 20.00 Uhr ', '', '', '', '', 'lecture', 2, 'Dr. Verena Böll', '', '', '', 0, 0, '', 1, NULL, 0, '58ad93706548e', 'de', '2017-02-22 14:34:40', '2017-03-24 21:46:04', '', ''),
('01c4e474-8f44-417b-b0fa-49c5a74153de', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', '„Wie geht’s?“ Language Animation for all', 'Basic training for youth leaders & educators\r\n\r\nThe participants learn in an active and practical way to know the method of language animation, they gain basics information about pedagogy of play and (trans) cultural learning. They may improve their competences and apply them on in five planned youth encounters. They will plan activities such as trips, handcraft work or cooking. Own initiatives from participants are very welcome.\r\nWhat is language animation?\r\nA method of learning a foreign language, which enables an intercultural exchange and helps to learn a new language in a playful way. The method helps to overcome language barriers and raises the motivation to learn. \r\n\r\nThe activities take place between March – October 2017.\r\nParticipant fee: 10 EUR, 5 EUR djo-members, refugees free of charge\r\nEach participant receives a certification of participation.\r\n\r\nFirst workshop on: 11. March 2017. 10:00 – 16:30\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5890bac3cfca9', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', NULL, NULL),
