('3189e1a1-0f26-4941-86b5-0a66222f4102', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Education Project of the Haus der Kongresse für Umwelt - Bau - Verkehr Dresden e.V. for Refugee Children and Adults', 'Saxony in climate change - seminars on the consequences of global warming for nature and the economy as well as on the possibilities of limiting consequences "\r\n \r\nThe educational project is aimed primarily at high school pupils, grammar schools and primary schools, as well as for teachers of biology and geography, as well as interested parties. It informs scientifically about the global and regional consequences of climatic changes as well as on individual and social requirements of a limitation of consequences.\r\n \r\nThe project organizer, as a state-certified forest teacher, as well as a natural and landscape guide, offers the Module 6 "Forest Educational Guided Tours" for refugees and the Module 7 "Medicinal plant migration" for adult refugees. For this purpose an interpreter / interpreter, who translates the translated contents correctly, is searched for.\r\n \r\nReport: info@sachsen-im-klimawandel.de', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57f941e7c671d', 'en', '2016-11-22 15:30:45', '2016-11-22 15:30:45', 'The educational project offers environment and atmosphere courses for refugee kids and adults.', NULL),
