('327bebb6-9714-4ec3-baff-9fbd76b790c9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, 'The Deutsche Hygiene-Museum is searching for asylum-seekers and refugees who are interested in giving a lecture or seminar in their area of expertise. The lectures will take place in August and September in Dresden. We invite refugees and asylum-seekers to share their knowledge and expertise with our audience in Dresden. A translation of the lectures with a translator is possible. dates: 24th an 31rd August, 14th and 28th September 2016, 7 pm', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5798a9a37f9f2', 'en', '2016-08-26 10:58:12', '2016-08-26 10:58:12', NULL, NULL),
