('35a46bd7-9bde-4e35-9b52-5a9b2f857e89', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, 'گروه پیشگامان Freifunk گروهی غیرتجاری است که شبکه‌های بی‌سیم رایگان ارائه می‌دهد. Freifunk در بسیاری از محل‌های اسکان درسدن در دسترس است.\r\n\r\nهر دو هفته یک‌بار ما وقت مشاوره برای Freifunk ارائه می‌دهیم.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '587fa7f0e2a87', 'fa', '2017-04-23 11:25:54', '2017-04-23 11:25:54', NULL, NULL),
('35a9bd3a-2def-4821-a5dd-27147fb9b2c2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'The Intercultural Sofa', 'We meet daily people from different nations and cultures, but most people know very little about their neighbors who either were born in Germany or had to flee from their country, who are waiting for their asylum or just want to study in Germany. \r\nTherefore there''s still a lot of stories to tell each other and discover and experience together.\r\n\r\nTo give this idea room to grow and to make a new atmosphere for people to meet each other, we made the intercultural Sofa, which should get rid of bias and turn it into more creativity.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '556e1d2a532e3', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:29:59', '2017-02-21 23:29:59', 'A meeting place for people from different nations and cultures. Here you can find no  prejudice.', NULL),
