('3b4d7611-1f9a-451f-bb58-3cdfd006cc70', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'To understand Islam - Seminar about the history, plurality and Islam in the 20th/21st century', 'The seminar offers a deeper thematic involvement with Islam, building on the talk “Den Islam verstehen – eine Einführung” (“To understand Islam – an introduction”).\r\nIt will be focused on the following:\r\n• Dynasties, Colonialism, Reforms\r\n• 20th/21st century: Islamic movements and organisations, crises, wars, Islamism, terror, flight and integration.\r\n3 x | 8 Units | free\r\n16H 1213', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57b1e96c0ece3', 'en', '2016-09-18 19:24:26', '2016-09-18 19:24:26', NULL, NULL),
