('3dba953d-e0bd-40ee-8cb0-63b7d1e42af3', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, 'The courses offered by LMI „Deutsch sofort“ are now also available to asylum seekers who are not eligible for an integration course (Integrationskurs). following, the course „Deutsch qualifiziert“ can be taken. Depending on the participants performance, the course will be completed with either a A2 or B1 certificate. Both courses together have a lenght of 600 lessons (one lesson 45 minutes). \r\nAnyone interested can register at LMI, and take the enty test.\r\n\r\nNIVEAU #a2 #b1 \r\nKOSTEN #kostenlos \r\nKURSART #deutschsofort #deutschqualifiziert \r\nABSCHLUSS #teilnahmebescheinigung #zertifikat_ger #dtz\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57e6b5a4a2734', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:28', '2017-03-20 14:01:28', 'German course for asylum seekers who don''t have access to Integration courses. Interested people can register immediately through LMI and and do a placement test.\r\n\r\nNIVEAU #A2 #B1 \r\nKOSTEN #kostenlos \r\nKURSART #deutschsofort #deutschqualifiziert \r\nABSCHLUSS #teilnahmebescheinigung #zertifikat_ger #dtz', NULL),
