('40430283-59c0-4a5a-a092-19d99c1a5b8d', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Women protection center Dresden e.V.', 'This offer is for  men and women, friends, or relatives who suffer from domestic/house violence, and professional helpers who want to help people having such problems.\r\n\r\nThe counseling is free, trustworthy, and if wanted anonymous.\r\n\r\nThere''s also the possibility to bring in interpreters/translators for every other language.\r\n\r\nOur emergency number:\r\n0351 - 281 77 88 \r\n \r\nTelephone counseling through the D.I.K(Dresden Intervention and Coordination Center for combating domestic violence in the immediate social environment) from Monday to Friday 8:00 to 16:00.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57cf067464120', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:08', '2017-02-21 23:30:08', 'The offer is directed towards the women and men, or friends or relatives  who want to support people who are prone to domestic violence.\r\n\r\nThe counselling is free, trusted and anonymous.\r\n\r\n#Frauen', NULL),
