('4522f667-3484-4035-8b76-506b34ec76c9', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'MehrGenerationenGarten APRIKOSEN FÜR ALLE - Apricot Garden', 'Gardens are places that offer protection and security in addition to very practical, multicultural activities, conversations, joint cooking on fire and events such as workshops, festivals and regular garden meetings. \r\n \r\nOur apricot garden invites particularly the people from the neighborhood to enjoy its view and help taking care of it. Working and having fun together is the main goal of this park, it''s a joint effort that opens the door for new creative ideas!', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5666e73fbbc3d', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:24', '2017-03-20 14:01:24', 'Gardens are places that provide protection and security, and in gardens you find a lot of activities like meeting new people, cooking together on the fire, and events like workshops, festivals and regular garden meetings.', NULL),
