('465db8cc-2da3-432e-8de4-953d12dba5ea', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Mobile Refugee Social Work', 'As part of the mobile refugee social work we advise and assist asylum seekers at the project locations Chemnitz and Dresden (Klotzsche, Neustadt, Pieschen, Südvorstadt). The tasks of the refugee social work include:\r\n\r\n - Developing life perspectives\r\n - Orientation assistance in Chemnitz and Dresden\r\n - Educating and giving information on asylum in Saxony\r\n - General social assistance and advice\r\n - Helping in conflict situations\r\n - Supporting with authority meetings\r\n - Accompanying to lawyers and other supporting structures\r\n - Helping with educational opportunities and dismantling language barriers\r\n - Refering to other consultation structures\r\n - Help finding health services\r\n - Accompanying volunteer structures for asylum seekers', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '58a35edacfab3', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', NULL, NULL),
