('4b8d14cf-fe90-42af-ae32-e0137557293a', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Country Report: SYRIA . Refugees talk about home', 'People from Syria, who have now found shelter in Dresden, will talk about how life was like in their homeland, the circumstances of their flight and their situation in Germany now. An event by the Society of Christ Church/Christuskirche in cooperation with Caritas Dresden.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '58a8bbe491175', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', NULL, NULL),
