('5c3935df-93e3-47c8-9b1f-7769107c7b29', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Contact-Impro Jam in Emmers', 'Once a month (1st Sunday, 7 pm) we Jam, i.e. we dance for Contact Improvisation. Open for everyone, we want to link the touch, dance, movement, and the soul together. Also works to break language barriers. \r\n \r\nThe Jam is a place of opportunities, a social experiment room for trying common dances in a group or with yourself, sometimes with musicians, sometimes without, often with music and with a manual at the start.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '560d283724839', 'en', '2016-04-18 21:08:39', '2016-06-21 17:23:02', NULL, NULL),
