('69437946-6181-4ed2-b383-dcfd6d918e1b', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'IDA - Initiative German Courses for Asylum Seekers', '''Initative für Deutschkurse für Asylsuchende'' is a project organized by students, and supported by employees of the Technical University of Dresden and other Dresdners.\r\nWe coordinate programs by students to help refugees (e.g. the Buddy-program), develop and coordinate projects for the integration of refugees (e.g. ABC-Tische or German courses or helping with homeworks), and promote intercultural exchange between refugees and students (e.g. through events or language courses from refugees to  students).\r\n\r\nYou can order a free booklet of our german courses through chirschwald@dresden.de or download through: \r\n\r\nhttp://slub.qucosa.de/api/qucosa%3A7737/attachment/ATT-0/', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '575dd5f5dad7e', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', '2017-02-21 23:30:07', 'The initiative for German Courses for Asylum Seekers (IDA) is an initiative by students, who coordinate helping offers for refugees, for example through Buddy-Programs and homework meetings, or through ABC-Tables and german courses, and encourages intercultural exchange.', NULL),
