('7ac67d90-91b7-4750-be90-49ad48b0fdbd', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Brücke/Most-Stiftung', 'The Brücke/Most-Stiftung is a foundation that was created in 1997 with the goal of working together with the Czech Republic and other east-European countries to support and finance them. For that purpose we do projects alone or with other partners, where people from different cultures can have a mutual experience.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '58a71b71ecf7e', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', '2017-03-20 14:01:30', NULL, NULL),
