('85a55a23-fecc-470f-826a-a8d723ea8778', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Ausländerrat Dresden e.V. - IBZ -International Meeting Center(Consulting)', 'Are you an immigrant and you have problems with authorities, your landlord or you employer? You received a letter and do not understand what it is or what to do?\r\nOur counselling center can be the first place for you to go in Dresden, and we can help you and if we couldn''t we can show you where you can get help.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '556e1d420242a', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:01', '2017-02-21 23:30:01', NULL, NULL),
