('adafab3e-3ad5-4a02-ad51-2783a59f5b8e', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'The Adventurous Playground "Panama"', 'PLAYING WITHOUT LIMITS\r\nIn the heart of Dresden Neustadt there is the adventurous playground “Panama” for children six years and up. There, they can play, climb, and jump around. Furthermore, there is a small vegetable garden. Different animals like goats, chicken, and horses live at “Panama”. The children take care of the animals and the plants. Parents are asked to accompany their children with at least one adult. \r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '585309a213c9a', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:10', '2017-02-21 23:30:10', 'The adventurous playground "Panama" lies in the middle of the Neustadt and is open for kids from 6 years old. Beside playing, kids can also take care of plants and animals there.', NULL),
