('b1afd96d-37ac-4630-8b9c-0fd52a608051', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Banda Internationale', 'We, a musical group from Dresden, are looking for interested people who\nwould like to make some music with us. We want to start a musical project\nfor several months, meet you every week, play songs from your countries\nand make a big concert in the end!\nAre you interested?\nDo you play an instrument? Are you a singer?\nPlease contact us and leave your name, contact, country and information about your\ninstrumental skills', '', '', '', '', '', 1, '', '', NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 1, '', 0, '55efe9bb3d98f', 'en', '2015-09-10 11:22:00', '2016-06-21 17:23:02', 'Banda Internationale is a band that makes music from the troubled regions of the world.\r\n\r\nWe''ve set out for the next 6 months to search for musicians among refugees and invite them to play and discover their music with us.', NULL),
