('bae14ced-9fc2-4379-83e0-04d8d7143aff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Language and cooking group: Social evening with Refugees', 'We, around 15-30 persons, play table tennis, table football, man-don''t-get-angry or chess. There''s a lot of conversing, some people explain some words, forms and official writings or legal documents for other people, or we just practice the German language.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57fe50b955049', 'en', '2016-11-22 15:30:45', '2016-11-22 15:30:45', 'Refugees, friends, acquaintances  and new faces meet each other regularly in a chill evening to play or talk together.', NULL),
