('c099c051-d175-4b87-8433-8452d6f8a21c', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Transition Facility for Refugees „Hauptschule am Ostpark“', 'The refugee accommodation in the old Hauptschule in Ostpark started its work in the 2nd of February  2015. Around 120 refugees came to it from places of war and crisis and have the chance to live there temporarily until they move out to their own rooms or  flats. "We welcome all people!" is our motto.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '588623e292054', 'en', '2017-04-23 11:25:16', '2017-04-23 11:25:16', NULL, NULL),
