('ca93abb7-1948-4549-9b79-60098da9f50b', NULL, 'adfb2457-819c-4574-ace1-56f5b38d8f96', 1, '', '', '', '', 'dresden', 'Climbing for ALL Dresden - Boulder City', 'We are a small group of climbers and bouldering people in Dresden. We would like climb together with refugees inside and outside around Dresden.\r\n\r\nBouldern is a kind of climbing. Bouldern means climbing along a wall	outside or inside a special house or room. It is a sport for people who want to push themselves to their limits or beyond. It just means having fun with other people. You don''t need special equipment, just climbing shoes to help secure footholds. If you are interested in trying that, you are welcome doing it with us.', 'climbingforall.dresden@gmail.com', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/climbingforall.dresden', '', 'sports', 0, 'Sascha Förster', '', '', '', 0, 0, 'de,en', 1, NULL, 1, '55f3e2b636279', 'de', '2015-09-12 10:30:46', '2017-04-12 19:22:43', 'We are a small group of climbers and bouldering people in Dresden. We would like climb together with refugees inside and outside around Dresden.', ''),
