('d1b35f5e-3221-428a-afe9-3c3b64f9b5f7', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'KulturLoge Dresden', 'The ''KulturLoge Dresden'' makes it possible for refugees and people with low incomes to have access to cultural and sport event.  \r\n\r\nUsually, the events are attanded together with a voluntary companion or mentor as a pair or as a group. The tickets will be picked up right at the ticket office of the event. Whether a game of ''Dynamo Dresden'' or ''Dresdner Eislöwen'', or an event in the ''Scheune'' or ''Staatsoperette'' - Kulturloge always has the right offers. To recieve tickets for an event together with one or a group of refugees, please contact KulturLoge.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '55786558b9c07', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:17', '2017-03-20 14:01:17', 'Free visits to cultural events with refugees. The KulturLoge Dresden allows people with low incomes to gert free access to cultural and sporting events. This includes, of course, asylum seekers.', NULL),
