('d6fea761-fccc-4d13-8065-3fe4ec3c93c1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Школа танцев для женщин и девочек', 'Мы приглашаем Вас танцевать! Народные танцы и хороводы. Все танцы легко учатся. Мы будем двигаться под красивую музыку и\r\nвеселиться вместе. Занятия бесплатные. Будем рады вас видеть!\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5813af09b8b25', 'ru', '2016-11-28 15:37:00', '2016-11-28 15:37:00', NULL, NULL),
('d71717df-905d-4d95-99dc-a461192c28a5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', NULL, 'The network „Bunte Neustadt“ (colorful Neustadt) is active in the area of Dresden Neustadt (including Albertstadt, Äußere and Innere Neustadt, Leipziger Vorstadt, Radeberger Vorstadt, and all neighboring communites) to:\r\n - support and coordinate volunteer work for refugees together with the Flüchtlingsrat\r\n - plan and execute projects and events for refugees\r\n- be the contact partner for volunteers, refugees, new ideas, and donations\r\n\r\nWe meet on a regular basis; please contact us for exact dates info@buerger-courage.de\r\n\r\nCurrent projects:\r\n - Arrangement of sponsorships\r\nTogether with the Flüchtlingsrat and the Cafe International we arrange sponsorships between refugees and volunteers. The goal is to establish a personal contact and improve the new start of the refugee in Germany. \r\nAre you (or several people together as a WG-sponsorship) interested in participating?\r\n\r\n - Language courses\r\nTogether with the Sprachlerninitiativen we provide voluntary language and conversation courses for refugees. Those are not a substitute for a professional German course, but they are an important additional help. \r\n\r\nAre you interested in providing a German course or participating in a language tandem-partnership (including activities like chess, cooking, city tours)?\r\n\r\n- Spaces to meet refugees\r\nWe want to organize different meetings for refugees and locals from the Neustadt (so far we did a family day in Panama e.V., or a BRN-breakfast). Those meetings should offer chances to get to know each other, share, play music, do sports, cook etc. \r\n\r\n- collecting bikes\r\nLike in other parts of the city, we want to collect bikes to repair them together with refugees\r\n\r\nFurther activities are planned and in progress:\r\n - Guided city tours for refugees\r\n - „HEIMlich schöner“ (improve the homes of refugees)\r\n - Support with the treatment of mentally ill/traumatized refugees\r\n\r\ncontact: info@buerger-courage.de\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '563940638dfc5', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:23', '2017-03-20 14:01:23', 'The Network "Bunte Neustadt"\r\n\r\n... supports and coordinates, with the Flüchtlingsrat, the voluntary involvement with refugees\r\n\r\n... plans and sets projects and events for and with refugees.', NULL),
('d73f016c-8f4f-4bcf-ada2-6986980cedc8', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'دروس اللغة الالمانية لطالبي اللجوء', 'الالمانية للمبتدئين: كل اثنين من الساعة 10:30 الى 12:00 و من 19:00 الى 20:30 و ايضا كل اربعاء من الـ 19:00 الى الـ 20:30 \r\nالموقع: Kinder- und Jugendhaus Chilli\r\n Österreicher Straße 54\r\n في Laubegast (اخر محطة للقطار رقم 4)\r\nليس بحاجة الى تسجيل مسبق\r\n\r\nKOSTEN #kostenlos\r\nKURSZEITEN #dienstags #mittwochs #vormittags #abends\r\nKURSART #frei', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5587ab834bbd4', 'ar', '2017-02-21 23:29:55', '2017-02-21 23:29:55', NULL, NULL),
('d752a1e4-fb44-4b05-ba48-097a204cb68f', NULL, 'adfb2457-819c-4574-ace1-56f5b38d8f96', 1, '', '', '', '', 'dresden', 'Deutsches Hygiene-Museum', 'Als Beitrag zu einer weltoffenen Willkommenskultur gewährt das Deutsche Hygiene-Museum Asylbewerbern freien Eintritt. Das Museum möchte den aus unterschiedlichen Gründen aus ihrer Heimat geflüchteten Menschen damit ein Angebot machen, am kulturellen Leben unserer Stadt Teil zu haben. In einer Kultureinrichtung wie dem DHMD werden die verbindenden Werte unserer demokratischen Gesellschaft vermittelt und die großen Fragen des Lebens in unserer Zivilisation diskutiert. Auch der Erwerb der deutschen Sprache kann durch die Wahrnehmung kultureller Angebote gefördert werden. Wir würden uns freuen, wenn viele Asylbewerber – ob allein oder mit ihren Familien – davon Gebrauch machen würden.', 'info@dhmd.de', 'http://www.dhmd.de', 'https://www.facebook.com/dhmdresden/', '0351 48460', 'museum', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 'de,en, fr, cs, pl', 1, NULL, 1, '571e2975eda1b', 'de', '2016-04-25 16:28:05', '2017-04-08 23:34:44', 'Als Beitrag zu einer weltoffenen Willkommenskultur gewährt das Deutsche Hygiene-Museum Asylbewerbern freien Eintritt. Das Museum möchte den aus unterschiedlichen Gründen aus ihrer Heimat geflüchteten Menschen damit ein Angebot machen, am kulturellen Leben unserer Stadt Teil zu haben.', ''),
('d775ab11-524e-4634-8a53-09f542de64cb', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'اداره‌ی بین‌الملل TU Dresden', 'اگر دانشجوی بین‌المللی هستید که می‌خواهید در TU Dresden‌ تحصیل کنید و یا اگر در حال حاضر در این دانشگاه دانشجو (میهمان، عادی، و یا دکتری) محسوب می‌شوید، اداره‌ی بین‌الملل یکی از اداره‌های مرکزی برای برقراری تماس است. چنانچه پرسشی پیرامون مدارک لازک جهت پذیرش، ثبت‌نام، فعالیت‌ها و رویدادهای فرهنگی و غیره دارید، به این اداره سر بزنید.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '57fc16a41f3cc', 'fa', '2017-04-12 17:29:38', '2017-04-12 17:29:38', NULL, NULL),
