('d7a511b4-6a90-4a98-b856-9481f05ad64e', NULL, '5dddf63d-ccf6-44e2-8daf-81bb44507fdd', 1, '', '', '', '', 'dresden', 'German Language Courses for Asylum Seekers', 'We offer beginner''s courses for German language for asylum seekers. The language course is free of charge for entitled people. Travel cost (monthly ticket) will be refunded. General learning materials/ books will be provided.\r\n\r\nParticipants: \r\nAsylum seekers from Syria, Iran, Iraq and Eritrea* who possess a stay permit or a certificate of registration as an asylum seeker (BüMA) and do not sufficiently speak, read or write German. \r\n*List of admitted countries of origin cans variate.\r\n\r\nDuration:\r\nThe duration of the course is 320 teaching hours and prepares for the certificate A1 German. There a 5 teaching lessons per day. It is possible to choose between morning or afternoon sessions.\r\n\r\nStart of the courses: \r\nWe will soon start new courses for asylum seekers! The first course starts on the 14.12.2015. \r\n\r\nCertificate: \r\nCertificate of participation German A1 level (european standard) \r\n\r\nFurther information: www.mediaproject.de or call us\r\n\r\n', 'missbach@mediaproject.de', 'http://www.mediaproject.de/', 'https://www.facebook.com/mediaprojectAG', '0351 34060 0', 'german-course-state', 0, 'Dr. Peter Mißbach', '', '', '', 0, 0, 'de,en', 0, NULL, 1, '5666e90e90619', 'de', '2015-12-08 15:28:30', '2017-04-08 23:29:30', 'Der Schwerpunkt unserer Deutschseminare ist die aktive Kommunikation. Trainiert werden vorrangig die klassischen Inhalte, wie die Verständigung mit deutschen Mitbürgern und Mitarbeitern, Geschäftspartnern und Behörden.\r\nBitte beachten Sie den Anmeldeschluss 14 Tage vor Seminarbeginn!', ''),
