('d90d1ad2-45f6-4a2c-9f0e-9c2899b2a630', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'German courses for refugee girls and women', 'We offer german language lessons for refugee women and girls in the Erstaufnahmeeinrichtung Hamburger Street and we''re always searching for new female helpers to help with teaching or to help us with child care. Our opening times are always Tuesday 16-17:30 and Saturday from 15-17:00. Registration is needed, but knowledge of teaching german is not.\r\n\r\n#Frauen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '56f3164d89f16', 'en', '2017-02-21 23:30:06', '2017-02-21 23:30:06', 'We offer German courses for refugee women and girls in the Hamburger Street Refugee Camp, and we''re currently looking for helpers who want to help us with child care. Registration is necessary, knowledge in teaching German is not.', NULL),
