('e0b5d563-da93-48d2-9cc7-eecbddbff7d3', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Woman "Hand in Hand"', 'A knitting-project with female refugees\r\nWe are a group of women who meet every Tuesday to knit and crochet together with women who are seeking refuge in Dresden.\r\nWhile doing some handiwork we get to know each other, exchange tips and improve our language skills. Wool and knitting needles are available for free. You are invited to bring your children!\r\n', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '5798ba2cc4295', 'en', '2016-09-02 11:37:08', '2016-09-02 11:37:08', 'A project for women who are seeking asylum in Dresden. We meet to do some hand work like knitting for example, and in addition to that we offer tips and we get to know each other to improve our language. We offer wool and knitting needles for free. We invite you and your kids as well!', NULL),
