('f334d1df-6b95-4422-be24-0b7c8432ed3b', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Atendi II - Consultation for Reugees', 'The Project "Atendi II" is a project to give advice and consultation for refugees in various aspects of the daily life. \r\n\r\nOur fields of activity are: \r\n\r\n- Mobile consultation in the counties\r\n- Establishing a Clearing procedure\r\n- Coordination of a psycho-social connection system\r\n- Coordination and consulting of voluntaries\r\n- Empowerment of asylum seekers and refugees in Saxony\r\n- Supporting and encouraging integration\r\n\r\nTarget group: \r\n\r\n- Asylum seekers and refugees\r\n- Civil society\r\n- Political actors and representatives inside of associations and civil society on a local, state, and federal levels', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '58a3637a0115e', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', '2017-03-20 14:01:29', 'The project „Atendi II“ includes counselling of refugees in their different life situations and the coordination of voluntary involvement. ', NULL),
