('f525e9ac-27ce-40b0-af92-0283b1ee56c1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'German- Meeting Saturday-Course', 'We offer a low-level German course twice a week as a first contact with the language. The course is open to everyone and can be joined at any time. On Thursdays it takes place at Bürgersaal of Ortsamt Prohlis from 10:00 - 11:00am and on Saturdays at Evangelische Kirchgemeinde Prohlis from 10:00 - 11:30am.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '566aaae578fe5', 'en', '2017-03-20 14:01:24', '2017-03-20 14:01:24', 'Twice a week we organize in Colorful Prohlis German courses for beginners that are open for everyone.', NULL);
